        <mxCell id="1e1lPeBxb3bEikpPYBq5-1007" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;b&gt;Deployment post processing:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Performs additional optimizations and cleanup steps after the build process, such as stripping symbols or thinning binaries, to prepare the app for release.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;b&gt;Strip debug symbols during copy:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Removes debug symbols when copying build products to reduce app size and protect internal implementation details.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;b&gt;Strip linked product:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Eliminates unused or debug-related symbols from the final linked binary to minimize size and improve performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
